### Teste da API no Railway
### Substitua YOUR_RAILWAY_URL pela URL real da sua aplicação

### 1. Health Check (deve funcionar sempre)
GET https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. Root Endpoint
GET https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. Swagger Documentation
GET https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/api-docs
Content-Type: application/json

### 4. Listar Jogos (público)
GET https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/api/jogos
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Cadastrar Usuário
POST https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/api/usuarios/cadastro
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "nome": "João Silva",
    "email": "joao@teste.com",
    "senha": "Teste123!",
    "confirmarSenha": "Teste123!"
}

### 6. Login
POST https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/api/usuarios/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "joao@teste.com",
    "senha": "Teste123!"
}

### 7. Listar Biblioteca (com token)
GET https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/api/biblioteca
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Comprar Jogo (com token)
POST https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/api/biblioteca/comprar
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "jogoId": "ID_DO_JOGO_AQUI"
}

### 9. Health Check Detalhado
GET https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/health/detailed
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Teste de Conectividade
GET https://YOUR_RAILWAY_URL/health/ping
Content-Type: application/json 